{"ID":"20220906204314-p407bzj","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906204314-p407bzj","title":"i-2限流","type":"doc","updated":"20220906204314"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204315-97v1qqj","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20220906204315-97v1qqj","updated":"20220906204315"}},{"ID":"20220906204316-1mqgfm7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204316-1mqgfm7","updated":"20220906204316"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.3 限流","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204317-edgea73","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204317-edgea73","updated":"20220906204317"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何为限流？为什么要限流？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204318-4rk18yn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204318-4rk18yn","updated":"20220906204318"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"针对软件系统来说，限流就是对请求的速率进行限制，避免瞬时的大量请求击垮软件系统。毕竟，软件系统的处理能力是有限的。如果说超过了其处理能力的范围，软件系统可能直接就挂掉了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204319-lborf64","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204319-lborf64","updated":"20220906204319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"限流可能会导致用户的请求无法被正确处理，不过，这往往也是权衡了软件系统的稳定性之后得到的最优解。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204320-mybh0s5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204320-mybh0s5","updated":"20220906204320"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"现实生活中，处处都有限流的实际应用，就比如排队买票是为了避免大量用户涌入购票而导致售票员无法处理。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204321-s6h6so4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204321-s6h6so4","updated":"20220906204321"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"排队示意图","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/f9f17071fc4d489d85d2a234fb298df1.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204322-iit36u6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204322-iit36u6","updated":"20220906204322"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"常见限流算法","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204323-sjdbqks","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204323-sjdbqks","updated":"20220906204323"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简单介绍 4 种非常好理解并且容易实现的限流算法！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204324-ax88s4r","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204324-ax88s4r","updated":"20220906204324"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204325-ynsh6tj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204325-ynsh6tj","updated":"20220906204325"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"图片来源于 InfoQ 的一篇文章","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://www.infoq.cn/article/Qg2tX8fyw5Vt-f3HH673","TextMarkTextContent":"《分布式服务限流实战，已经为你排好坑了》"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204326-uhvyobo","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204326-uhvyobo","updated":"20220906204326"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"固定窗口计数器算法","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204327-7pjdsk5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204327-7pjdsk5","updated":"20220906204327"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"固定窗口其实就是时间窗口。","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"固定窗口计数器算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 规定了我们单位时间处理的请求数量。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204328-zleng7k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204328-zleng7k","updated":"20220906204328"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"假如我们规定系统中某个接口 1 分钟只能访问 33 次的话，使用固定窗口计数器算法的实现思路如下：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204329-7shhgaq","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204329-7shhgaq","updated":"20220906204329"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204330-zpof808","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204330-zpof808","updated":"20220906204330"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204331-css1t2a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204331-css1t2a","updated":"20220906204331"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"给定一个变量 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"counter"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 来记录当前接口处理的请求数量，初始值为 0（代表接口当前 1 分钟内还未处理请求）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204332-xuq4y0o","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204332-xuq4y0o","updated":"20220906204332"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204333-80ig1pv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204333-80ig1pv","updated":"20220906204333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 分钟之内每处理一个请求之后就将 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"counter+1"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，当 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"counter=33"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 之后（也就是说在这 1 分钟内接口已经被访问 33 次的话），后续的请求就会被全部拒绝。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204334-t24vx00","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204334-t24vx00","updated":"20220906204334"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204335-kk4qxbt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204335-kk4qxbt","updated":"20220906204335"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"等到 1 分钟结束后，将 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"counter"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 重置 0，重新开始计数。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204336-q97y53l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204336-q97y53l","updated":"20220906204336"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这种限流算法无法保证限流速率，因而无法保证突然激增的流量。"}]},{"ID":"20220906204337-j19ek0b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204337-j19ek0b","updated":"20220906204337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"就比如说我们限制某个接口 1 分钟只能访问 1000 次，该接口的 QPS 为 500，前 55s 这个接口 1 个请求没有接收，后 1s 突然接收了 1000 个请求。然后，在当前场景下，这 1000 个请求在 1s 内是没办法被处理的，系统直接就被瞬时的大量请求给击垮了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204338-frmj7ah","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204338-frmj7ah","updated":"20220906204338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"固定窗口计数器算法","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://static001.infoq.cn/resource/image/8d/15/8ded7a2b90e1482093f92fff555b3615.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204339-pwc04ho","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204339-pwc04ho","updated":"20220906204339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"滑动窗口计数器算法","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204340-x0bqjh0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204340-x0bqjh0","updated":"20220906204340"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"滑动窗口计数器算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 算的上是固定窗口计数器算法的升级版。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204341-mib37qp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204341-mib37qp","updated":"20220906204341"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"滑动窗口计数器算法相比于固定窗口计数器算法的优化在于：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"它把时间以一定比例分片"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204342-fagragq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204342-fagragq","updated":"20220906204342"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"例如我们的接口限流每分钟处理 60 个请求，我们可以把 1 分钟分为 60 个窗口。每隔 1 秒移动一次，每个窗口一秒只能处理 不大于 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"60(请求数)/60（窗口数）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的请求， 如果当前窗口的请求计数总和超过了限制的数量的话就不再处理其他请求。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204343-cg42u7v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204343-cg42u7v","updated":"20220906204343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"很显然， ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"当滑动窗口的格子划分的越多，滑动窗口的滚动就越平滑，限流的统计就会越精确。"}]},{"ID":"20220906204344-xsr0c85","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204344-xsr0c85","updated":"20220906204344"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"滑动窗口计数器算法","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://static001.infoq.cn/resource/image/ae/15/ae4d3cd14efb8dc7046d691c90264715.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204345-tv21qyd","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204345-tv21qyd","updated":"20220906204345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"漏桶算法","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204346-ix1u0ze","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204346-ix1u0ze","updated":"20220906204346"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们可以把发请求的动作比作成注水到桶中，我们处理请求的过程可以比喻为漏桶漏水。我们往桶中以任意速率流入水，以一定速率流出水。当水超过桶流量则丢弃，因为桶容量是不变的，保证了整体的速率。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204347-cexzi6a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204347-cexzi6a","updated":"20220906204347"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果想要实现这个算法的话也很简单，准备一个队列用来保存请求，然后我们定期从队列中拿请求来执行就好了（和消息队列削峰/限流的思想是一样的）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204348-t29dh6w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204348-t29dh6w","updated":"20220906204348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"漏桶算法","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://static001.infoq.cn/resource/image/75/03/75938d1010138ce66e38c6ed0392f103.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204349-3r0jvx3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204349-3r0jvx3","updated":"20220906204349"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"令牌桶算法","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204350-e7v3kr2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204350-e7v3kr2","updated":"20220906204350"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"令牌桶算法也比较简单。和漏桶算法算法一样，我们的主角还是桶（这限流算法和桶过不去啊）。不过现在桶里装的是令牌了，请求在被处理之前需要拿到一个令牌，请求处理完毕之后将这个令牌丢弃（删除）。我们根据限流大小，按照一定的速率往桶里添加令牌。如果桶装满了，就不能继续往里面继续添加令牌了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204351-6sbhexm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204351-6sbhexm","updated":"20220906204351"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"令牌桶算法","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://static001.infoq.cn/resource/image/ec/93/eca0e5eaa35dac938c673fecf2ec9a93.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204352-lo164iy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204352-lo164iy","updated":"20220906204352"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"单机限流","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204353-ezgh7lx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204353-ezgh7lx","updated":"20220906204353"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"单机限流可以直接使用 Google Guava 自带的限流工具类 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"RateLimiter"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"RateLimiter"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 基于令牌桶算法，可以应对突发流量。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204354-g16ooko","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204354-g16ooko","updated":"20220906204354"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204355-zc0v7ho","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204355-zc0v7ho","updated":"20220906204355"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Guava 地址：https://github.com/google/guava","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204356-40hfaqw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204356-40hfaqw","updated":"20220906204356"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除了最基本的令牌桶算法(平滑突发限流)实现之外，Guava 的","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"RateLimiter"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"还提供了 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"平滑预热限流"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的算法实现。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204357-uigg1eu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204357-uigg1eu","updated":"20220906204357"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"平滑突发限流就是按照指定的速率放令牌到桶里，而平滑预热限流会有一段预热时间，预热时间之内，速率会逐渐提升到配置的速率。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204358-pts7bpe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204358-pts7bpe","updated":"20220906204358"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们下面通过两个简单的小例子来详细了解吧！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204359-4jha1uq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204359-4jha1uq","updated":"20220906204359"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们直接在项目中引入 Guava 相关的依赖即可使用。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204360-jnu95ry","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"eG1s","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906204360-jnu95ry","updated":"20220906204360"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eG1s","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\u003cdependency\u003e\n    \u003cgroupId\u003ecom.google.guava\u003c/groupId\u003e\n    \u003cartifactId\u003eguava\u003c/artifactId\u003e\n    \u003cversion\u003e31.0.1-jre\u003c/version\u003e\n\u003c/dependency\u003e\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204361-tx67c0w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204361-tx67c0w","updated":"20220906204361"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面是一个简单的 Guava 平滑突发限流的 Demo。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204362-rajpgzl","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906204362-rajpgzl","updated":"20220906204362"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import com.google.common.util.concurrent.RateLimiter;\n\n/**\n * 微信搜 JavaGuide 回复\"面试突击\"即可免费领取个人原创的 Java 面试手册\n *\n * @author Guide哥\n * @date 2021/10/08 19:12\n **/\npublic class RateLimiterDemo {\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        // 1s 放 5 个令牌到桶里也就是 0.2s 放 1个令牌到桶里\n        RateLimiter rateLimiter = RateLimiter.create(5);\n        for (int i = 0; i \u003c 10; i++) {\n            double sleepingTime = rateLimiter.acquire(1);\n            System.out.printf(\"get 1 tokens: %ss%n\", sleepingTime);\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204363-8ef9ci1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204363-8ef9ci1","updated":"20220906204363"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"输出：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204364-extvzp2","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"YmFzaA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906204364-extvzp2","updated":"20220906204364"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"YmFzaA==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"get 1 tokens: 0.0s\nget 1 tokens: 0.188413s\nget 1 tokens: 0.197811s\nget 1 tokens: 0.198316s\nget 1 tokens: 0.19864s\nget 1 tokens: 0.199363s\nget 1 tokens: 0.193997s\nget 1 tokens: 0.199623s\nget 1 tokens: 0.199357s\nget 1 tokens: 0.195676s\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204365-ppempq8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204365-ppempq8","updated":"20220906204365"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面是一个简单的 Guava 平滑预热限流的 Demo。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204366-eibguj4","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906204366-eibguj4","updated":"20220906204366"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import com.google.common.util.concurrent.RateLimiter;\nimport java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit;\n\n/**\n * 微信搜 JavaGuide 回复\"面试突击\"即可免费领取个人原创的 Java 面试手册\n *\n * @author Guide哥\n * @date 2021/10/08 19:12\n **/\npublic class RateLimiterDemo {\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        // 1s 放 5 个令牌到桶里也就是 0.2s 放 1个令牌到桶里\n        // 预热时间为3s,也就说刚开始的 3s 内发牌速率会逐渐提升到 0.2s 放 1 个令牌到桶里\n        RateLimiter rateLimiter = RateLimiter.create(5, 3, TimeUnit.SECONDS);\n        for (int i = 0; i \u003c 20; i++) {\n            double sleepingTime = rateLimiter.acquire(1);\n            System.out.printf(\"get 1 tokens: %sds%n\", sleepingTime);\n        }\n    }\n}\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204367-paednmw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204367-paednmw","updated":"20220906204367"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"输出：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204368-ovz0kbr","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"YmFzaA==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906204368-ovz0kbr","updated":"20220906204368"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"YmFzaA==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"get 1 tokens: 0.0s\nget 1 tokens: 0.561919s\nget 1 tokens: 0.516931s\nget 1 tokens: 0.463798s\nget 1 tokens: 0.41286s\nget 1 tokens: 0.356172s\nget 1 tokens: 0.300489s\nget 1 tokens: 0.252545s\nget 1 tokens: 0.203996s\nget 1 tokens: 0.198359s\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204369-31kvdp0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204369-31kvdp0","updated":"20220906204369"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Bucket4j"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一个非常不错的基于令牌/漏桶算法的限流库。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204370-q26o8q7","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204370-q26o8q7","updated":"20220906204370"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204371-s9jy8uw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204371-s9jy8uw","updated":"20220906204371"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Bucket4j 地址：https://github.com/vladimir-bukhtoyarov/bucket4j","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204372-xawb91x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204372-xawb91x","updated":"20220906204372"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相对于，Guava 的限流工具类来说，Bucket4j 提供的限流功能更加全面。不仅支持单机限流和分布式限流，还可以集成监控，搭配 Prometheus 和 Grafana 使用。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204373-25blnit","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204373-25blnit","updated":"20220906204373"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不过，毕竟 Guava 也只是一个功能全面的工具类库，其提供的开箱即用的限流功能在很多单机场景下还是比较实用的。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204374-3w1r910","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204374-3w1r910","updated":"20220906204374"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spring Cloud Gateway 中自带的单机限流的早期版本就是基于 Bucket4j 实现的。后来，替换成了 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Resilience4j"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204375-qu572t9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204375-qu572t9","updated":"20220906204375"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Resilience4j 是一个轻量级的容错组件，其灵感来自于 Hystrix。自","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://github.com/Netflix/Hystrix/commit/a7df971cbaddd8c5e976b3cc5f14013fe6ad00e6","TextMarkTextContent":"Netflix 宣布不再积极开发 Hystrix"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 之后，Spring 官方和 Netflix 都更推荐使用 Resilience4j 来做限流熔断。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204376-7ptp6ql","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204376-7ptp6ql","updated":"20220906204376"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204377-6dy8mvo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204377-6dy8mvo","updated":"20220906204377"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Resilience4j 地址: https://github.com/resilience4j/resilience4j","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204378-4s7bhss","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204378-4s7bhss","updated":"20220906204378"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一般情况下，为了保证系统的高可用，项目的限流和熔断都是要一起做的。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204379-hgx135a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204379-hgx135a","updated":"20220906204379"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Resilience4j 不仅提供限流，还提供了熔断、负载保护、自动重试等保障系统高可用开箱即用的功能。并且，Resilience4j 的生态也更好，很多网关都使用 Resilience4j 来做限流熔断的。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204380-3f14730","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204380-3f14730","updated":"20220906204380"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因此，在绝大部分场景下 Resilience4j 或许会是更好的选择。如果是一些比较简单的限流场景的话，Guava 或者 Bucket4j 也是不错的选择。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204381-zdyoyge","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204381-zdyoyge","updated":"20220906204381"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分布式限流","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204382-7zj0t4x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204382-7zj0t4x","updated":"20220906204382"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分布式限流常见的方案：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204383-w8cqc5f","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204383-w8cqc5f","updated":"20220906204383"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204384-si3cip6","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204384-si3cip6","updated":"20220906204384"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204385-cw4hlte","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204385-cw4hlte","updated":"20220906204385"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"借助中间件架限流"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：可以借助 Sentinel 或者使用 Redis 来自己实现对应的限流逻辑。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204386-8hmm03m","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204386-8hmm03m","updated":"20220906204386"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204387-ltdh3tb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204387-ltdh3tb","updated":"20220906204387"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"网关层限流"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：比较常用的一种方案，直接在网关层把限流给安排上了。不过，通常网关层限流通常也需要借助到中间件/框架。就比如 Spring Cloud Gateway 的分布式限流实现","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"RedisRateLimiter"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"就是基于 Redis+Lua 来实现的，再比如 Spring Cloud Gateway 还可以整合 Sentinel 来做限流。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204388-ncsqu1k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204388-ncsqu1k","updated":"20220906204388"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果你要基于 Redis 来手动实现限流逻辑的话，建议配合 Lua 脚本来做。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204389-4e9spyb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204389-4e9spyb","updated":"20220906204389"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"网上也有很多现成的脚本供你参考，就比如 Apache 网关项目 ShenYu 的 RateLimiter 限流插件就基于 Redis + Lua 实现了令牌桶算法/并发令牌桶算法、漏桶算法、滑动窗口算法。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204390-ewiiuwb","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204390-ewiiuwb","updated":"20220906204390"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204391-t2248hu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204391-t2248hu","updated":"20220906204391"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ShenYu 地址: https://github.com/apache/incubator-shenyu","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204392-qr8xdfv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204392-qr8xdfv","updated":"20220906204392"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/e1e2a75f489e4854990dabe3b6cec522.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204393-8wsln8y","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204393-8wsln8y","updated":"20220906204393"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相关阅读","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204394-mf7qoox","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204394-mf7qoox","updated":"20220906204394"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204395-50szf6n","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204395-50szf6n","updated":"20220906204395"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204396-d9jktzk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204396-d9jktzk","updated":"20220906204396"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"服务治理之轻量级熔断框架 Resilience4j ：https://xie.infoq.cn/article/14786e571c1a4143ad1ef8f19","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204397-anqjj0b","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204397-anqjj0b","updated":"20220906204397"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204398-vxd8v2p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204398-vxd8v2p","updated":"20220906204398"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"超详细的 Guava RateLimiter 限流原理解析：https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1408819","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204399-vzxaw6f","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204399-vzxaw6f","updated":"20220906204399"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204400-19c2mwr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204400-19c2mwr","updated":"20220906204400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实战 Spring Cloud Gateway 之限流篇 👍：https://www.aneasystone.com/archives/2020/08/spring-cloud-gateway-current-limiting.html","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]}]}